<content>1 Problems

1.1 Creating a new page is almost impossible
* No menu allows this (yet)
* When adding a new link in an existing page [New] the resulting link is broken (xpage=--- is bad):
   http://89.34.62.77:8080/xwiki/bin/edit/XWiki/New?parent=XWiki.Problems&amp;xpage=---
* Only way that works is to enter the right url by hand
* Fixed. Make a patch for trunk?

1.1 Login: No error message on wrong password
* When you try to log-in and something goes wrong you must be informed about it
* Fixed. Committed to trunk.

1.1 Adding Attachments Fails
* 300k, 170k
* see [Problem.html&gt;http://89.34.62.77:8080/xwiki/bin/download/XWiki/Problems/Problem.html] (small attachment) for the error message. Not the same as the error message for too large attachments [AttachmentTooLarge.html&gt;http://89.34.62.77:8080/xwiki/bin/download/XWiki/Problems/AttachmentTooLarge.html].
* same error for changing picture/avatar

1.1 Diff between the same version causes error

~~From Version 1.31 to 1.31 edited by XWiki Admin on 2006/07/31 11:30~~

~~Error number 13005 in 13: Error while making meta object diff of Main.WebHome between version 1.31 and version 1.31 Wrapped Exception: null~~

1.1 Visual editor has many problems in Safari
Q: Is this a problem of the edit control or of XWiki ?
* Typing enter at the end of the first line deletes the last character
* Selecting &amp; applying format does not work
* many many other

1.1 Links: Problems with UNICODE
* http://89.34.62.77:8080/xwiki/bin/view/Sandbox/TestTopic1
* [The JIRA task|http://jira.xwiki.org/jira/browse/XWIKI-188]
</content>
